<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>31</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kan Bawi Jesuh kan ih hlanah, huhphenh nak kha kan in hal, Misual kan
 si run kan zaangfah, Kannih run kan thian-ter tuah.

[V2]
 Nihin ah kan palh sualmi kha, Bawipa run kan thlahpiak tuah! Keimah
 kha run ka zaangfah tuah, Nangmah bantuk si ka duh.

[V3]
 Kan ih kar ah kan pawngkam ah, Tih awk kha um hmanhseh law, Vanmi nih
 an kan zohkhenh ca'h, Zeihmanh kha kan tih lai lo.

[V4]
 Tu zan ah thi hmanh u si law, Kannih ca zei a poi lo, Thaizing ah na
 vancung khua ah, Kan thlarau aa hlau cang lai.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<title>ZANLEI THLACAMNAK CH31</title>
</song>